#: xfce4-notifyd/main.c:62
msgid ""
"Your Wayland compositor does not support required protocol wlr-layer-shell."
msgstr "Wayland compositor ຂອງທ່ານບໍ່ຮອງຮັບໂປຣໂຕຄໍ wlr-layer-shell ທີ່ຈຳເປັນ."

#: xfce4-notifyd/main.c:69
msgid "xfce4-notifyd was built without support for your windowing system."
msgstr "xfce4-notifyd ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍບໍ່ຮອງຮັບລະບົບຈັດການໜ້າຕ່າງຂອງທ່ານ."

